Package: ribobaser
Title: Organizes functions to work with read counts extracted from
    RiboBase
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("CenikLab", email = "ccenik@austin.utexas.edu", role = c("cre") )
Description: Given matched RNA-seq and ribosome profiling read
    counts—typically obtained from RiboBase—this package offers utilities
    for quality control, data aggregation, and translation efficiency
    calculation.
